name: com.unity.template.hd
description:
This template utilizes the High Definition Render Pipeline. Making it a good starting point for people focused on high-end graphics that want to develop games for platforms that support Shader Model 5.0 (DX11 and above). 

Beyond being tuned for High End visuals this project includes
▪ Shadergraph 
▪ Visual Effect Graph  
▪ Presets 
▪ Example content
